      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t八十年前，中国大陆还是中华民国，而台湾岛是日本<br/>\n八十年后的现在，中国大陆被称为中华人共和国，而台湾岛成了中华民国<br/>\n金门和马祖是唯二的一直是中华民国的地方。<br/>\n所以我认为”中华民国人“是他们最适合的自我认同<br/>\n顺便放一张老图<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS8yd3J1YVlLLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/2wruaYK.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/2wruaYK.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2wruaYK.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
      "date": "2023-08-26",
      "agree_count": 10,
      "discussion_count": 2,
      "discussions": [
        {
          "id": "1203639",
          "replier": {
            "username": "ji3g4z04wj06",
            "uid": "77840"
          },
          "date": "2023-08-28",
          "content": "笑死"
        },
        {
          "id": "1203728",
          "replier": {
            "username": "烏龍珍珠奶蓋",
            "uid": "73293"
